property.name: Text 1
property.value: Hey... You don't look like you're from around here... What are you doing here?

property.name: Text 2
property.value: Howdy, many things changed since you last been here... You might find somthing.... concerning

property.name: Text 3
property.value: Did you know I was the first ever guy down here?

property.name: Text 4
property.value: I hate kids who thinks they can just waltz down here..

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Huh? What's a navi like you doing down here? Lookin' fer trouble? Then how about lookin fer Wiltman, he sure would love to meet you...

property.name: Text 1
property.value: I see you got a sense of adventure in your programming! Nice, I'm Pyreman.EXE! I'm here to make burning data bits out of the annoying problem down here from Wiltman.... Hey I know! You should help us! He wouldn't stand a chance against an army! My bud Cyanman's HP is in the next area and would hook you up with something cool! But he locked his HP so you need a password... I forgot what it would be... I just know it's a name of a fire chip...

property.name: Text 1
property.value: I saw some hothead just walk into the void without flying.... How did he do that?

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Can't you see I'm busy here! Move it!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Beat it! Wiltman doesn't want annnnnnyyy interruptions today! He will deal with you another day....

property.name: Text 1
property.value: . . . What is he even doing? He's just walking back and forth like a moron!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Oh that guy? I told him if he wants to date me; he gotta lose some weight first... I said it as a joke to get him to go away, but he's really determined... I like that in a guy.

property.name: Text 1
property.value: THE UNDERSQUARE IS UP! I'M HERE TO MAKE SURE A CERTAIN TROUBLE MAKER DOESN'T COME BACK! OOOOO WHEN I SEE HIM I'MA WACK HIM IN THE NOGGIN WITH THIS BUSTER I FOUND!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Hey, I'm sellin sum chocolate chips... Pretty rare if you think about it, my 'Op makes them every Saturday night, 1,000 zenny for just 5 of them! C'mon I know you're interested..... What? you don't want any?? Suit your self!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Hehehehe.... I just pulled off a big prank! I spent months collecting Molokos and let em all out in the square! Bwahahahah! You shoulda seen their faces!!!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Welcome to Killobyte Prices! Here's what I got in stock!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Bah! Some stupid punks mugged me of my zenny! You better watch out for yourself...

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Psst, hey! You! You look like you can take a hit or two... How about a fight?

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Bah such a shame... But I'll be here if you change your mind.

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Nice, always appreciate each layer it has.

property.name: Text 1
property.value: ... You'd better get out of my sight little man.

property.name: Text 1
property.value: THIS LEADS TO THE RESIDENTIAL AREA! HOME AREA, HANG OUTS, STORES AND A PLANNED SECRET! IM NOT ALLOWED TO SAY WHAT THAT IS, BUT GET GOING!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: I herd there's a shape shiftin key that changes forms; "Where you speak". It "unlocks gates in your path".... Where is it? I herd it's infront of a text board or somthin...

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Drat! I was gonna buy this lot but someone beat me to it! Now I gotta try somewhere else...

property.name: Text 1
property.value: ...Huh? Me? Doin Nothing at all kid, I'm just minding my business here.. heh heh...

property.name: Description
property.value: THIS CUBE IS FOR ADMINS ONLY! IF YOU ARE NOT A ADMIN THEN LEAVE!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Sorry kid, this area is offline at the moment...

property.name: Text 1
property.value: I AM SORRY, BUT THE OWNER OF THIS PLACE WANTS NO OUTSIDERS TO GET IN! IF YOU ALREADY DON'T KNOW HOW TO GET IN, THAT MEANS YOU ARENT SUPPOSED TO BE IN THERE!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Did you know the password for Cyanman's cube is Burrito's? Sounds silly doesnt it?

property.name: Description
property.value: HELLO IM A PROG STUCK IN THIS CUBE! I AM HERE TO BLOCK PEEPERS FROM ACESSING A FUN AREA THAT THEY ARE TOO EARLY FOR! ITS FOR CHRISTMAS PURPOSES ONLY! COME BACK... UH LIKE 2 MONTHS LATER?

property.name: Text 1
property.value: I wonder when that portal will be fixed... It's been a few months now....huh? where does it lead too? Its for the junction! A way to travel to diffrent parts of the net without needing outside help. Very useful if you ask me! This means I could go to Chip King!
